{"tid":2323230,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK ROSÉ領養流浪狗取名Hank！開通專用IG帳號一天漲粉35萬","createTime":"2020-12-13T04:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T12:36:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":94,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f76425b77e2f59449befff8220c436ce1c3c0105","tid":2323230,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"ROS&Eacute;真的好有愛心！這隻名叫Hank的狗狗也真的很可愛，期待看到更多更新呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nROS&Eacute;本月10日在自己的IG上PO出一張狗狗照片，介紹新的家庭成員：「我是Hank，請多多指教！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_01e5e889e94eb8bc4f5da22797e0c527/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132269-888594.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_01e5e889e94eb8bc4f5da22797e0c527%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132269-888594.png&h=8a7ea15c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來ROS&Eacute;不久前從江陵保護所領養了一隻被遺棄的狗狗，當時狗狗狀態很不好、病的很重，需要住院3個月才能痊癒，看起來好可憐：<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7cad4f7bb7aa8d4020ab2760a4a33caf/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132269-888595.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7cad4f7bb7aa8d4020ab2760a4a33caf%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132269-888595.jpg&h=4c061364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時救護者給它起名叫Mir，這是它住在保護所時的樣子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9f14956a9478f95865885885b06fd953/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132269-888598.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9f14956a9478f95865885885b06fd953%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132269-888598.png&h=a41b0914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幸好現在Mir被ROS&Eacute;一家領養，終於可以在安穩的環境中好好生活啦：<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_17cb91d39c26f2a92011d51c27a7b83a/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132269-888599.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_17cb91d39c26f2a92011d51c27a7b83a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132269-888599.png&h=cc5b8cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經為Mir擔任臨時照護的人也PO文表示很開心它找到了「可以相伴一輩子的家人」：<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9b2d106305c8046b16e0b2c1c8f542a5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132269-888600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9b2d106305c8046b16e0b2c1c8f542a5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132269-888600.png&h=1283f206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nROS&Eacute;給狗狗起名Hank，還為Hank開通了單獨的IG帳號，現在粉絲數已經超過50萬啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_068e4f171d1daf61042f06bf4082497d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132269-888601.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_068e4f171d1daf61042f06bf4082497d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132269-888601.png&h=5b32743a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這幾天ROS&Eacute;經常在Hank的帳號裡分享照片和影片，看來除了在家玩，也經常帶Hank出門散步，Hank看起來好有活力！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f1006206538604d4f397ca45e59c6372/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132269-888607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f1006206538604d4f397ca45e59c6372%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132269-888607.jpg&h=b0bc36fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c11f28d1d87f373e6efdf7d62d593544a7f4258c","tid":2323230,"uid":16659,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"還有和BLACKPINK另外兩位成員Jisoo、Lisa同Hank的合照！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a1bf362917713a2e52125e4cf2090f36/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132269-888603.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a1bf362917713a2e52125e4cf2090f36%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132269-888603.png&h=93fe4147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_940df